https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=16905	31800
3D打印技术现在飞速进入新的领域——从<a href="http://www.blueprintmagazine.co.uk/index.php/architecture/the-worlds-first-printed-building/">打印整座建筑物</a>到<a href="http://www.inhabitat.com/2010/01/20/mits-digital-food-printer-creates-nutritious-meals/">打印食物</a>，现在科学家又用3D打印机<a href="http://www.inhabitat.com/2010/03/22/scientists-use-3d-printer-to-create-first-printed-human-vein/">“打印”出人体血管</a>。<i>
